Requirements
    • Identify a single dog up to 150’ away
    • Position the camera to keep the target within the image
        ◦ Exception – If the target is momentarily inside of or behind an object, the camera must be able to reacquire once visual is reestablished
    • Power supply shall be easily changed/replaced
    • Power supply shall be at least one battery
    • A secondary device may be used in conjunction with the automated mount for final video capture (Aka Christina’s iPhone)
